{"id":4272,"count":12,"description":"<h2>Peru<\/h2>\r\nColorful and vibrant Peru: home to one of the seven wonders of the world, and bucket-list favorite, Machu Picchu! The first view of the lost Incan city, as it shines through the clouds, is pure magic. Journey to the summit of rich green mountains, surrounded by hundreds of llamas, and smiling locals wearing bright, multicolored ponchos. An incredible experience!\r\n\r\nHowever, Peru has even more to give. It is a country featuring beautiful cities, with interesting backstories. For instance, Arequipa with its unique volcanic stone buildings. Or Lima, with its streets that act as a time capsule to the past. After a walk through history, there is nothing left to do but admire the hypnotizing landscapes that exist in every direction. From vast deserts to rainbow mountains, and everything in between.\r\n<h3>Modern Peru<\/h3>\r\nNow, in modern-day Peru, there is a special union between ancient history and the future. Days can easily pass by appreciating city street art or drinking in contemporary coffee shops. All while singing along to the background sound of traditional Peruvian pan pipes. Consequently, there is no doubt that Peruvians know how to live, breathe, eat, and dance in color! Peru\u2019s constant colorful evolution is just another reason that the country remains a timeless, travel favorite.","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/","name":"Peru","slug":"peru","taxonomy":"category","parent":0,"meta":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Peru Travel Guides &amp; Tips - Salt in our Hair Blog<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Colorful and vibrant Peru: home to one of the seven wonders of the world: Machu Picchu! Get to know its incredible destinations.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-vid